data.description:
Welcome to this beautifully updated home nestled in the Rockfish area of Raeford! Enjoy modern living with a fully renovated kitchen featuring new cabinets, butcher block countertops, shelving, and updated appliances. The bedrooms boast new LVP flooring, providing both style and durability. 

 Convenience is key with its proximity to Raeford/Fayetteville shopping and the upcoming 295 extension, ensuring swift commuting to Fort Liberty. Situated on a cul-de-sac, this home offers a spacious backyard perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. 

Showings start on 12/11, book your private tour today!
